      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this incredible project opportunity! While this vehicle is in poor condition and will require some significant mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get back to its prime, it's the perfect blank canvas for a dedicated restorer. If you're looking for a budget-friendly way to build your dream car from the ground up, this is the one for you!",
