      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and there\u2019s not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It still has that fresh new-car smell and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I'm looking for a quick, smooth sale, so feel free to reach out with any questions. You seriously won't find another one this clean!",
