      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant with individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system and documented rod bearing replacement, ensuring peak mechanical integrity. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally optimized with proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Bilstein dampers. Finished in Alpine White, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero oxidation, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather with no bolster wear. This is a turnkey, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist seeking a benchmark E46.",
